### Working Group Introductions (DECON & REGEXT)
*   **Domain Connect (DECON):** Peter Thomason introduced the newly chartered working group. DECON is an application-level protocol allowing SaaS providers to request automatic DNS record configuration in customer zones via templates. The group focuses on transitioning change control from GoDaddy/the community to the IETF while maintaining backward compatibility.
*   **Registration Extensions (REGEXT):** James Galvin introduced the working group, which recently transitioned from the ART area to the OPS area. REGEXT covers extensions to Extensible Provisioning Protocol (EPP) and Registration Data Access Protocol (RDAP). Current hot topics include RDAP extensions, EPP over QUIC/HTTP, and domain variant support for Internationalized Domain Names (IDNs).

